#| "on the web.}"
msgid ""
"\\warning{Although \\application{Evolution} can be used with many webmail "
"systems, such as Yahoo! Mail, Hotmail, and Gmail, you may prefer to use the "
"\\application{Firefox} web browser to access them.}"
